{"_id":"6FlQO0u8yXnaCI2G","name":"A Toast to Death","content":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<h1 class=\"wide\">A Toast to Death</h1>\n<p>Arni Amill offers to sell the group three units worth of wine for just $100 per unit on the condition the wine is only sold in a pirate town. He claims it is a peace offering to pirate crews to leave Wrasseton alone—in fact he has a far more sinister plan.</p>\n<p>Following the death of his family Arni began plotting his revenge. The wine has been doctored with a slow-acting but deadly poison. The once mild-mannered Arni is planning an act of genocide. Each mug of wine requires the drinker to make a Vigor roll. Failure results in death within 2d6 hours.</p>\n<p>The group can find a buyer on a successful Streetwise roll. A Persuasion roll is required to determine the price. On a success the buyer offers $300 per unit increasing by $100 for each raise.</p>\n<p>Within a matter of days several hundred pirates die from the deadly brew. Sadly for the characters, the pirates blame them and come looking for the poisoners. Several pirate captains collectively place a bounty of 1,000 pieces of eight on each character’s head.</p>\n<p>On any encounter with pirates—on land or at sea—draw an additional card. If the card is black the pirates have heard of the poisoning and seek revenge on the group.</p>\n</div>","img":"https://assets.forge-vtt.com/5f43f8ea1a91d63438d13159/artwork-adventures/pirates-of-cyre/icons/pirates-of-cyre.webp","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"DX8acFfCTTwwzgWq":3},"flags":{"journal-links":{"references":{}},"monks-enhanced-journal":{"_viewcount":1,"scrollPos":"{\".description\":0}"},"cf":{"id":"temp_slwk1t4xhcl","path":"Mourners of Lhazaar#/CF_SEP/Savage Tales","color":"#000000"},"_document-sheet-registrar":{}}}
{"_id":"6ViM09GZEwwZ5v8z","name":"Hiers Ivanov","content":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p><strong>Skills: </strong>Smuggler, Divination spells</p>\n<p><strong>Appearance (besides image): </strong>always with a hoodie,</p>\n<p><strong>Personality: </strong>Elusive</p>\n<p><strong>How she met Trucco: </strong>Was the one who helped Trucco escape Metrol at the time. Had a couple of interactions while selling stolen goods.</p>\n<p><strong>Last interaction/rumor:</strong> Never heard from them again after escaping Metrol. A couple of months prior, she was acting nervous, as if she had a bad premonition or something, Trucco believes she knew about The Mourning through a vision.</p>\n</div>","img":"https://assets.forge-vtt.com/5f43f8ea1a91d63438d13159/artwork-bestiary/humanoids/changeling/changeling-01.webp","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"DX8acFfCTTwwzgWq":3},"flags":{"monks-enhanced-journal":{"type":"person","relationships":[],"scrollPos":"{\".tab.details .tab-inner\":0,\".tab.description .tab-inner\":0,\".relationships .items-list\":0}","role":"","location":"Unknown","race":"Changeling","gender":"","age":"","pronoun":"","eyes":"","skin":"","hair":"White","profession":"","voice":"","faction":"","height":"","weight":"","traits":"","ideals":"","bonds":"","flaws":"","longterm":"","shortterm":"","beliefs":"","secret":"","_lasttab":"relationships","fields":{"race":{"value":true},"gender":{"value":true},"age":{"value":true},"eyes":{"value":true},"skin":{"value":false},"hair":{"value":true},"pronoun":{"value":true},"profession":{"value":false},"voice":{"value":true},"faction":{"value":false},"height":{"value":false},"weight":{"value":false},"traits":{"value":true},"ideals":{"value":false},"bonds":{"value":false},"flaws":{"value":true},"longterm":{"value":true},"shortterm":{"value":true},"beliefs":{"value":true},"secret":{"value":true}}},"_document-sheet-registrar":{"type":"person"},"journal-backlinks":{"references":{}},"cf":{"id":"temp_6nu2k3j5j03","path":"Mour