{"_id":"8579PWn4dLL6v9kV","name":"Something in the Bilges","content":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<h1 class=\"wide\">Something in the Bilges</h1>\n<p>The PCs should not be assigned duty in the bilges today. If such work is indicated, roll again to find new tasks for the PCs.</p>\n<p>At about mid-morning on the fourth day, Giffer Tibbs rushes onto deck. A successful @Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-skills.Notice]{Notice} check can see his ashen face as well as overhear what he reports to Mr. Lagraa. Giffer was below on rat-catching duty when something big swam out of the bilge water and bit him. Lagraa immediately looks for volunteers to investigate, and selects all of the new pirates (including the cook’s mate), telling them to get down to the @Compendium[savage-tales-pirates-of-cyre.pirates-of-cyre-tales.Bilges]{bilges} and not bother coming out until whatever is down there is dead.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>@Compendium[savage-eberron-bestiary.savage-eberron-bestiary.Rat, Dire]{Dire Rats} (6)</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Tactics</h3>\n<p>Six dire rats have gnawed their way out of a dodgy consignment of barley the captain picked up in Regalport on the cheap, and have taken up residence in the brackish water in the bilges. Today the weather is so blistering that the bilges are considered @Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Heat]{very hot}. A rat is found every [[/r (1d6)*(1d8+4)]] minutes while down in the bilges. Swabs must make a @Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-skills.Notice]{Notice} (–4) or be @Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Surprise]{surprised} when the rats strike from the water.</p>\n<h3>Treasure</h3>\n<p>Searching of the @Compendium[savage-tales-pirates-of-cyre.pirates-of-cyre-tales.Bilges]{bilges} could reward the swabs with the items that are forgotten down there.</p>\n<h2 class=\"aftermath\">Aftermath</h2>\n<p>If the swabs spend more than 4 hours in the bilges, Mr. Lagraa sends one of the pirates down to tell them if they can’t deal with one tiny creature in half an hour, they each get three lashes. If the swabs fail to kill all of the rats, they’re likely to bite someone else, an event that earns the swabs three lashes each. In that case, the following day Mr. Lagraa automatically assigns only one swab (to prevent time wasting) to the bilges again.</p>\n</div>","img":"https://assets.forge-vtt.com/5f43f8ea1a91d63438d13159/artwork-adventures/pirates-of-cyre/icons/pirates-of-cyre.webp","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"DX8acFfCTTwwzgWq":3},"flags":{"journal-links":{"references":{}},"monks-enhanced-journal":{"_viewcount":1},"quick-encounters":{"quickEncounter":"{\"journalEntryId\":\"MMMTZcygBDdHuIMw\",\"extractedActors\":[{\"numActors\":1,\"dataPackName\":\"savage-tales-pirates-of-cyre.pirates-of-cyre-bestiary\",\"actorID\":\"KEeR7YOKnWikm2I1\",\"name\":\" Krornik Kragshard\",\"savedTokensData\":[],\"generatedTokensData\":[{\"actorId\":\"KEeR7YOKnWikm2I1\",\"isSavedToken\":false}],\"combinedTokensData\":[{\"actorId\":\"KEeR7YOKnWikm2I1\",\"isSavedToken\":false}]}],\"hideQE\":true,\"qeVersion\":\"0.8.4\"}"},"cf":{"id":"temp_72m1iiovqki","path":"Mourners of Lhazaar#/CF_SEP/Season 1: Mutiny Against the Cloudreavers#/CF_SEP/The Storm Reaver Savage Tales","color":"#000000"}}}
