{"_id":"IJ50uKvBPIqcOK84","name":"Cargo Hold","content":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<h1 class=\"wide\">Cargo Hold</h1>\n<p>This is the ship’s cargo hold. The hold is mostly empty at the start of the adventure, save for the 14 pigs; normally kept caged, they periodically escape and run loose within the hold.</p>\n<p>The ceiling is open to the @Compendium[savage-tales-pirates-of-cyre.pirates-of-cyre-tales.Weapons Deck]{Weapons Deck} so cargo may be raised and lowered. There is a locked door in the aft wall that leads to the @Compendium[savage-tales-pirates-of-cyre.pirates-of-cyre-tales.Officers Quarters]{Officers Quarters}. Towards the bow there are double doors that lead to the @Compendium[savage-tales-pirates-of-cyre.pirates-of-cyre-tales.Brig]{Brig} as well as a hall passage with ladders up to the @Compendium[savage-tales-pirates-of-cyre.pirates-of-cyre-tales.Weapons Deck]{Weapons Deck}.</p>\n<p>@Compendium[savage-tales-pirates-of-cyre.pirates-of-cyre-bestiary.Owlbear Hartshorn]{Owlbear Hartshorn} is invariably chained to the near the @Compendium[savage-tales-pirates-of-cyre.pirates-of-cyre-tales.Officers Quarters]{Officers Quarters} to keep him from causing trouble and to keep people out.</p>\n</div>","img":"https://assets.forge-vtt.com/5f43f8ea1a91d63438d13159/artwork-adventures/pirates-of-cyre/icons/pirates-of-cyre.webp","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"DX8acFfCTTwwzgWq":3},"flags":{"journal-links":{"references":{}},"core":{"sourceId":"JournalEntry.L91WkUzg75E8tVjM"},"cf":{"id":"temp_dljw0qnmnui","path":"Mourners of Lhazaar#/CF_SEP/Season 1: Mutiny Against the Cloudreavers#/CF_SEP/The Storm Reaver#/CF_SEP/Locations on the Storm Reaver","color":"#000000"}}}
{"_id":"Id9QqpdZvQJmMrRq","name":"Crater","content":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p><strong>Skills:</strong> Strength and toughness, Berserk</p>\n<p><strong>Appearance (besides image):</strong> tall with wide shoulders, grayish eyes, expressionless face.</p>\n<p><strong>Personality:</strong> Stoic, Few words, but loves really bad jokes and laughs out loud whenever he hears them.</p>\n<p><strong>How he met Trucco:</strong> Early member of the Hrazhak team that Trucco later joined. They were friends until he got kicked out of the team after being blamed for Trucco’s pickpocketing.</p>\n<p><strong>Last interaction/rumor:</strong> Joined the war efforts. Heard he betrayed an official and run away from a battle, but anyone who really knows Crater thinks that can’t possibly be true.</p>\n</div>","img":"https://assets.forge-vtt.com/5f43f8ea1a91d63438d13159/artwork-bestiary/humanoids/shifter/shifter-male-01.webp","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"DX8acFfCTTwwzgWq":3},"flags":{"monks-enhanced-journal":{"type":"person","relationships":[],"_lasttab":"description","role":"","location":"Unknown","race":"Shifter","gender":"Male","age":"","pronoun":"He/Him","eyes":"Gray","skin":"","hair":"","profession":"","voice":"","faction":"","height":"","weight":"","traits":"","ideals":"","bonds":"","flaws":"","longterm":"","shortterm":"","beliefs":"","secret":"","fields":{"race":{"value":true},"gender":{"value":true},"age":{"value":true},"eyes":{"value":true},"skin":{"value":false},"hair":{"value":true},"pronoun":{"value":true},"profession":{"value":true},"voice":{"value":true},"faction":{"value":false},"height":{"value":false},"weight":{"value":false},"traits":{"value":true},"ideals":{"value":false},"bonds":{"value":false},"flaws":{"value":true},"longterm":{"value":true},"shortterm":{"value":true},"beliefs":{"value":true},"secret":{"value":true}},"scrollPos":"{\".tab.details .tab-inner\":0,\".tab.description .tab-inner\":0,\".relationships .items-list\":0}"},"_document-sheet-