{"_id":"JBrneClXhXYT5ZGX","name":"The Storm Reaver Crew","content":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<h1 class=\"wide\">The Storm Reaver Crew</h1>\n<p>Use this chart to track how the characters are influencing other pirates on the <em>Storm Reaver.</em></p>\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th class=\"main-heading\" colspan=\"5\">Crew Disposition</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th class=\"sub-heading left\">Name</th>\n<th class=\"sub-heading left\">Role</th>\n<th class=\"sub-heading left\">Stat</th>\n<th class=\"sub-heading left\">Disposition</th>\n<th class=\"sub-heading left\" style=\"width:30%\">Notes</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th class=\"bar-heading\" colspan=\"5\"><span class=\"no-class\">Officers</span></th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>@Compendium[savage-tales-pirates-of-cyre.pirates-of-cyre-tales.Officers of the Storm Reaver]{Mika Rockface}</td>\n<td>@Compendium[savage-tales-pirates-of-cyre.pirates-of-cyre-tales.Ship Roles]{Captain}</td>\n<td>F dwarf</td>\n<td>Hostile</td>\n<td>Ignores characters</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>@Compendium[savage-tales-pirates-of-cyre.pirates-of-cyre-tales.Officers of the Storm Reaver]{Mister Lagraa}</td>\n<td>@Compendium[savage-tales-pirates-of-cyre.pirates-of-cyre-tales.Ship Roles]{First Mate}</td>\n<td>F orc</td>\n<td>Hostile</td>\n<td>Replaces the human Mr. Plugg; Lagraa is a figure to be hated; suspicious of everyone</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>@Compendium[savage-tales-pirates-of-cyre.pirates-of-cyre-tales.Officers of the Storm Reaver]{Master Scourge}</td>\n<td>@Compendium[savage-tales-pirates-of-cyre.pirates-of-cyre-tales.Ship Roles]{Boatswain / Master-at-Arms}</td>\n<td>M half-orc</td>\n<td>Hostile</td>\n<td>Turned into a half-orc from a human; a sadistic coward that uses connect with Mr. Lagraa for power and protection</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>@Compendium[savage-tales-pirates-of-cyre.pirates-of-cyre-tales.Officers of the Storm Reaver]{Krornik \"Fishguts\" Kragshard}</td>\n<td>@Compendium[savage-tales-pirates-of-cyre.pirates-of-cyre-tales.Ship Roles]{Cook}</td>\n<td>M dwarf</td>\n<td>Neutral</td>\n<td>Replaces the human Ambrose Kroop</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>@Compendium[savage-tales-pirates-of-cyre.pirates-of-cyre-tales.Officers of the Storm Reaver]{\"Cut-Throat\" Grok}</td>\n<td>@Compendium[savage-tales-pirates-of-cyre.pirates-of-cyre-tales.Ship Roles]{Quartermaster}</td>\n<td>F half-orc</td>\n<td>Neutral</td>\n<td> </td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>@Compendium[savage-tales-pirates-of-cyre.pirates-of-cyre-tales.Officers of the Storm Reaver]{Grovus Stormbeard}</td>\n<td>@Compendium[savage-tales-pirates-of-cyre.pirates-of-cyre-tales.Ship Roles]{Sorcerer}</td>\n<td>M dwarf</td>\n<td>Unfriendly</td>\n<td>Replaces peppery Longfarthing; Rockface inner circle</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>@Compendium[savage-tales-pirates-of-cyre.pirates-of-cyre-tales.Officers of the Storm Reaver]{Riaris Krine}</td>\n<td>@Compendium[savage-tales-pirates-of-cyre.pirates-of-cyre-tales.Ship Roles]{Master Gunner}</td>\n<td>M orc</td>\n<td>Unfriendly</td>\n<td>Rockface inner circle</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>@Compendium[savage-tales-pirates-of-cyre.pirates-of-cyre-tales.Officers of the Storm Reaver]{Hakrilli Quarne}</td>\n<td>@Compendium[savage-tales-pirates-of-cyre.pirates-of-cyre-tales.Ship Roles]{Artificer/Carpenter/Healer}</td>\n<td>F dwarf</td>\n<td>Unfriendly</td>\n<td>Rockface inner circle</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>@Compendium[savage-tales-pirates-of-cyre.pirates-of-cyre-tales.Officers of the Storm Reaver]{Gragoth}</td>\n<td>@Compendium[savage-tales-pirates-of-cyre.pirates-of-cyre-tales.Ship Roles]{Gunner's mate}</td>\n<td>M orc</td>\n<td>Hostile</td>\n<td>Replaces Kipper, bootlicker to Lagraa and Scourge</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>@Compendium[savage-tales-pirates-of-cyre.pirates-of-cyre-tales.Officers of the Storm Reaver]{Patch \"Salty\" Kolkrinun}</td>\n<td>@Compendium[savage-tales-pirates-of-cyre.pirates-of-cyre-tales.Ship Roles]{Boatswain's mate}</td>\n<td>F dwarf</td>\n<td>Hostile</td>\n<td>Replaces Patch Patchsalt, sycophant to Lagraa and Scourge</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>@Compendium[s