{"_id":"N9YPOpmxldrvkLkh","name":"Forecastle","content":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<h1 class=\"wide\">Forecastle</h1>\n<p>This raised deck stands some 10 feet above the main deck, immediately behind the bowsprit, which is shaped like a rearing dragon spitting lightning. The foremast rises 30 feet above this deck.</p>\n</div>","img":"https://assets.forge-vtt.com/5f43f8ea1a91d63438d13159/artwork-adventures/pirates-of-cyre/icons/pirates-of-cyre.webp","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"DX8acFfCTTwwzgWq":3},"flags":{"journal-links":{"references":{}},"cf":{"id":"temp_dljw0qnmnui","path":"Mourners of Lhazaar#/CF_SEP/Season 1: Mutiny Against the Cloudreavers#/CF_SEP/The Storm Reaver#/CF_SEP/Locations on the Storm Reaver","color":"#000000"}}}
