{"_id":"wsEngBMZrmQDGZnQ","name":"Zero","content":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p><strong>Skills:</strong> Originally designed for house cleaning and dictation.</p>\n<p><strong>Appearance (besides image): </strong>Gold ornaments and clean design, not designed for war.</p>\n<p><strong>Personality: </strong>Calm and introspective, always asking metaphysical questions whenever they find the chance.</p>\n<p><strong>How they met Trucco: </strong>Zero was tossed out of his household, the reason being that they were “malfunctioning and asking too many questions instead of working”. Trucco helped them to get a new life on a ship to the Lhazaar Principalities.</p>\n<p><strong>Last interaction/rumor: </strong>Went on a ship to Lhazaar Principalities. Never heard from them since.</p>\n</div>","img":"https://assets.forge-vtt.com/5f43f8ea1a91d63438d13159/artwork-bestiary/humanoids/warforged/warforged-merchant-02.webp","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"DX8acFfCTTwwzgWq":3},"flags":{"monks-enhanced-journal":{"type":"person","relationships":[],"role":"","location":"Lhazaar Principalities","race":"Warforged","gender":"","age":"6","pronoun":"They/Them","eyes":"","skin":"","hair":"","profession":"","voice":"","faction":"","height":"","weight":"","traits":"","ideals":"","bonds":"","flaws":"","longterm":"","shortterm":"","beliefs":"","secret":"","scrollPos":"{\".tab.details .tab-inner\":0,\".tab.description .tab-inner\":0,\".relationships .items-list\":0}","_lasttab":"details","fields":{"race":{"value":true},"gender":{"value":true},"age":{"value":true},"eyes":{"value":true},"skin":{"value":false},"hair":{"value":true},"pronoun":{"value":true},"profession":{"value":true},"voice":{"value":true},"faction":{"value":false},"height":{"value":false},"weight":{"value":false},"traits":{"value":true},"ideals":{"value":false},"bonds":{"value":false},"flaws":{"value":true},"longterm":{"value":true},"shortterm":{"value":true},"beliefs":{"value":true},"secret":{"value":true}}},"_docume