{"_id":"x8KEsuvQEOs2afyM","name":"Hand of Plenty","content":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<p>The <em>Hand of Plenty</em> is a pleasure yacht: a floating casino, performance hall, and bordello all in one. Once, it belonged to a prince no one sings songs about anymore. Now it sails independent, able to make enough profits with its services to buy protection from its host principalities.</p>\n</div>","img":"modules/monks-enhanced-journal/assets/organization.png","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"DX8acFfCTTwwzgWq":3},"flags":{"monks-enhanced-journal":{"type":"organization","_lasttab":"relationships","relationships":[{"type":"place","id":"jD9VwVKBwJ2p0vUg","relationship":"Primary Berth","hidden":false},{"type":"person","id":"ZkCVPU2FgtudRujy","relationship":"Captain and Propietor","hidden":false},{"id":"cD2iHikSpmmCPimk","hidden":false}],"alignment":"","location":"","scrollPos":"{\".tab.description .tab-inner\":0}"},"_document-sheet-registrar":{"type":"organization"},"journal-backlinks":{"references":{}},"cf":{"id":"temp_dabx38xqa7","path":"Mourners of Lhazaar Lore#/CF_SEP/Lhazaar Principalities#/CF_SEP/02.09.13. Vessels","color":"#6d0000"}}}
